Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}同じ二人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:54.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}まばたく刹那　君を想うよ
